%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20track%20goods%20so%20companies%20can%20ensure%20their%20supply%20chains%20are%20resilient%20has%20raised%20a%20%2430%20million%20Series%20B%20funding%20round%20led%20by%20Notion%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclean-energy-jobs-climate-tech-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETreefera%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20developed%20a%20platform%20that%20pulls%20in%20satellite%20and%20drone%20images%20of%20the%20so-called%20first%20mile%20of%20supply%20chains%20%E2%80%94%20the%20initial%20starting%20point%20from%20which%20goods%20are%20transported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%20is%20for%20this%20data%20to%20create%20transparency%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20products%20such%20as%20coffee%20or%20palm%20oil%20to%20help%20companies%20comply%20with%20decarbonization%20targets%20and%20ESG%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purpose%20of%20Treefera%20is%20to%20provide%20discoverable%2C%20understandable%2C%20and%20trustworthy%20datasets%20on%20the%20first%20mile.%20From%20forestry%20to%20agriculture%2C%20it's%20about%20massively%20scaling%20up%20our%20direct%20observation%20of%20that%20first%20mile%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Horn%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Treefera%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20AI%20platform%20gathers%20other%20real-world%20information%20about%20a%20supply%20chain's%20first%20mile%2C%20such%20as%20carbon%20metrics%2C%20environmental%20insights%2C%20and%20land%20records.%20That%20data%20is%20then%20packaged%20up%20into%20its%20platform%2C%20which%20customers%20can%20then%20access%20through%20application%20programming%20interfaces%2C%20or%20APIs%2C%20said%20Treefera%20cofounder%20Caroline%20Grey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20layers%20of%20sourcing%2C%20which%20means%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20a%20land%20file%2C%26quot%3B%20Grey%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThen%20we%20provide%20lots%20of%20data%20on%20sourcing%2C%20risk%20data%2C%20various%20other%20inputs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-tech-startups-data-center-boom-ai-funding-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etougher%20funding%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20climate%20and%20climate-adjacent%20startups%2C%20Treefera%20has%20bucked%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20aren't%20many%20other%20startups%20in%20this%20space%2C%20and%20we're%20tackling%20a%20compelling%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Grey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Notion%20Capital%2C%20the%20Series%20B%20attracted%20investment%20from%20Endeit%20Capital%20and%20follow-on%20funding%20from%20Albion%20VC%2C%20Triple%20Point%2C%20and%20Twin%20Path%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fresh%20funding%2C%20Treefera%20plans%20to%20accelerate%20its%20product%20releases%20and%20expand%20further%20in%20Europe%20and%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%2010-slide%20deck%20Treefera%20used%20to%20raise%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Treefera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683db0b0ca50259add4d6f68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETreefera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Treefera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683db0b0c6ad288d14824d9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETreefera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Treefera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683db0b06ffb6822ec61e133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3