mary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20decided%20to%20provide%2020%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Agniveers%20in%20direct%20recruitment%20to%20several%20positions%20in%20the%20state%20police%20force%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Our%20kids%20don't%20get%20an%20allowance%20for%20chores.%20Surprisingly%2C%20they've%20never%20pushed%20back%20on%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224857%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kids%20helping%20each%20other%20put%20away%20dishes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683a08ff6ffb6822ec61d57e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20kids%20(not%20pictured)%20do%20chores%20without%20getting%20an%20allowance.%3Cp%3EMariya%20Borisova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20used%20to%20try%20to%20take%20care%20of%20everything%20in%20my%20household%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20something%20had%20to%20give.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20started%20asking%20our%20three%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20ages%2014%2C%2011%2C%20and%205%20%E2%80%94%20to%20start%20pitching%20in%20with%20chores.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20don't%20pay%20them%20an%20allowance%20for%20helping%20out.%20They're%20learning%20it's%20just%20part%20of%20being%20a%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20house%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaying-kids-for-chores-allowances-entitlement-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20pay%20our%20kids%20to%20do%20chores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20no%20allowance%20tied%20to%20emptying%20the%20trash%20and%20no%20reward%20system%20for%20sweeping%20the%20floor.%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20that%20might%20sound%20rigid%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20even%20unfair.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20this%20decision%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intentional%20things%20we've%20done%20as%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20mom%20of%20three%20%E2%80%94%20ages%2014%2C%2011%2C%20and%205%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20carry%20the%20full%20load.%20I'd%20cook%20dinner%2C%20clean%20the%20kitchen%2C%20do%20laundry%20for%20five%20people%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-running-business-tips-work-life-balance-find-time-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20my%20own%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20still%20stay%20emotionally%20available%20to%20everyone.%20Like%20many%20parents%2C%20I%20thought%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20it%20all%26quot%3B%20was%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20But%20eventually%2C%20I%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20something%20had%20to%20give.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22150b728d-ef31-42db-aa68-42d94fee0e0d%5C%22%3EWe%20decided%20to%20try%20a%20different%20approach%20to%20household%20chores%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20He%20works%20long%20hours%20and%20often%20gets%20home%20late%2C%20so%20we%20divided%20up%20responsibilities%20in%20a%20way%20that%20made%20sense%20for%20our%20family.%20He's%20in%20charge%20of%20yard%20work%20and%20playing%20with%20the%20kids%20in%20the%20evenings.%20I%20cook%20and%20clean%20up%20after%20dinner%20and%20take%20care%20of%20all%20the%20laundry%2C%20including%20washing%20and%20putting%20away%20clothes%20for%20myself%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20our%20youngest%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20household%20doesn't%20just%20sit%20back%20and%20relax.%20Our%20kids%20have%20daily%20responsibilities%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20because%20we're%20trying%20to%20raise%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20domestic%20superheroes.%20We're%20simply%20trying%20to%20raise%20capable%2C%20aware%20humans%20who%20understand%20that%20homes%20don't%20run%20on%20autopilot%2C%20and%20that%20being%20part%20of%20a%20family%20means%20pulling%20your%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20introduced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-parent-allowance-salary-teaches-kids-save-give-money-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20of%20chore%20assignments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20wrote%20out%20every%20task%20that%20needed%20to%20get%20done%20each%20day.%20I%20let%20my%20two%20older%20kids%20take%20turns%20picking%20from%20the%20list%2C%20rotating%20back%20and%20forth%20until%20everything%20was%20claimed.%20That%20way%2C%20no%20one%20could%20complain%20they%20got%20stuck%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%26quot%3B%20job.%20It%20was%20fair%2C%20it%20was%20clear%2C%20and%20it%20gave%20them%20ownership%20right%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20our%2014-year-old%20takes%20the%20laundry%20to%20the%20basement%20where%20our%20washer%20and%20dryer%20live%2C%20collects%20the%20household%20trash%2C%20sweeps%20the%20main%20floor%20rugs%2C%20and%20keeps%20his%20room%20clean.%20Our%2011-year-old%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20cleaning%20the%20toilets%20(a%20hero's%20job%2C%20let's%20be%20honest)%2C%20replacing%20toilet%20paper%20rolls%2C%20bringing%20in%20the%20mail%2C%20putting%20away%20clean%20dishes%2C%20and%20keeping%20his%20room%20tidy.%20And%20our%205-year-old%20daughter%20feeds%20the%20dogs%20dinner%2C%20organizes%20the%20shoes%20at%20our%20front%20door%2C%20and%20puts%20away%20her%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%2C%20we%20don't%20give%20them%20money%20for%20any%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20chores%20are%20simply%20part%20of%20being%20a%20member%20of%20our%20household.%20You%20live%20here%2C%20you%20contribute.%20That's%20the%20expectation%20%E2%80%94%20not%20as%20punishment%20or%20control%2C%20but%20because%20we%20all%20benefit%20from%20a%20clean%2C%20functional%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20we're%20not%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-earn-money-street-performers-busking-fund-dream-trips-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids%20earning%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20one%20of%20our%20children%20wants%20to%20earn%20spending%20money%20to%20buy%20something%2C%20we%20give%20them%20the%20opportunity%2C%20but%20through%20bigger%20chores%20like%20babysitting%20their%20younger%20sister%20while%20we%20work%2C%20weed-whacking%20the%20yard%2C%20walking%20the%20dogs%2C%20or%20tackling%20a%20larger%20cleaning%20project.%20We're%20teaching%20them%20that%20money%20is%20earned%20through%20extra%20effort%2C%20not%20handed%20out%20for%20doing%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22863a3130-6d4a-4205-8de7-1d3bedc7ee81%5C%22%3EThis%20system%20has%20had%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20our%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprised%20me%20most%20about%20this%20system%20is%20how%20little%20resistance%20we%20get.%20It's%20become%20routine%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20up%20for%20debate.%20And%20because%20we've%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20chores%20are%20not%20a%20punishment%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20just%20part%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20days%2C%20all%20the%20kids'%20chores%20combined%20take%20about%2015%20minutes.%20But%20the%20impact%20has%20been%20tremendous%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20on%20my%20own%20mental%20load%20(though%20yes%2C%20that's%20real%20and%20important)%2C%20but%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-give-our-kids-independence-in-stages-but-they-also-have-responsabilities-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids'%20sense%20of%20ownership%20and%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20don't%20roll%20their%20eyes%20when%20I%20ask%20them%20to%20sweep%20or%20take%20out%20the%20trash.%20They%20just%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mom%2C%20I%20see%20how%20this%20structure%20is%20quietly%20shaping%20their%20character.%20They're%20learning%20time%20management%2C%20responsibility%2C%20pride%20in%20their%20space%2C%20and%20even%20a%20bit%20of%20gratitude%2C%20because%20they%20understand%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20keep%20a%20household%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20doesn't%20come%20with%20Pinterest-perfect%20chore%20charts%20or%20daily%20incentives.%20It's%20not%20flashy.%20But%20it%20works.%20And%20it's%20helped%20restore%20some%20peace%20and%20balance%20to%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20it's%20sending%20a%20message%20that%20I%20hope%20sticks%20with%20them%20into%20adulthood%3A%20you%20don't%20get%20paid%20just%20for%20showing%20up.%20You%20show%20up%20because%20it's%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20And%20when%20you%20want%20more%20%E2%80%94%20more%20money%2C%20more%20responsibility%2C%20more%20freedom%20%E2%80%94%20you%20work%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20lesson%20we're%20trying%20to%20teach%20in%20our%20home.%20And%20it%20starts%20with%20a%20trash%20can%2C%20a%20broom%2C%20a%20toilet%20brush%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20trust%20that%20these%20little%20things%20will%20add%20up%20to%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-pay-kids-allowance-do-household-chores-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748942221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683a08ff6ffb6822ec61d57e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-pay-kids-allowance-do-household-chores-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%203%20kids%20do%20household%20chores%20and%20we%20don't%20pay%20them%20allowance%20for%20it.%20This%20system%20is%20teaching%20them%20about%20responsibility%20and%20pulling%20their%20weight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Hope%20Denton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-pay-kids-allowance-do-household-chores-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assad%20Regime%20Detained%20