6ad288d14824b5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDefense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth's%20attendance%20at%20the%20Shangri-La%20Dialogue%20was%20the%20second%20Trump%20administration's%20big%20chance%20to%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20its%20plans%20in%20Asia%20Pacific.%3Cp%3ELudovic%20MARIN%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Shangri-La%20Dialogue%20is%20the%20top%20summit%20in%20Asia%20for%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20military%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20meet%20every%20year%20at%20a%20famed%20hotel%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Singapore%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%2C%20Pete%20Hegseth%20accused%20China%20of%20preparing%20for%20war%2C%20while%20Beijing%20sent%20in%20a%20downgraded%20team.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20early%20on%20a%20Friday%20morning%2C%20the%20world's%20men%20and%20women%20of%20war%20were%20already%20collecting%20their%20keycards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%2022%20years%2C%20the%20Shangri-La%20Hotel%20in%20Singapore%20has%20hosted%20what's%20become%20Asia's%20biggest%20defense%20summit%2C%20which%20ran%20this%20year%20from%20May%2030%20to%20June%201.%20The%20Shangri-La%20Dialogue%20is%20an%20annual%20mass%20gathering%20of%20military%20leaders%2C%20with%20generals%20and%20ministers%20from%2047%20countries%20flooding%20into%20the%20792-room%20hotel%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20the%20war%20chiefs%20of%20five%20continents%20spent%20three%20days%20in%20elaborate%2C%20carefully%20choreographed%20diplomacy.%20Defense%20contractors%20dipped%20in%20and%20out%20of%20conference%20rooms%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%20hoping%20to%20catch%20customers%20amid%20the%20flurry%20of%20closed-door%20bilateral%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20outside%20was%20simple%20but%20tight.%20One%20road%20leads%20into%20the%20Shangri-La%2C%20and%20one%20road%20leads%20out.%20Pairs%20of%20assault%20rifle-wielding%20men%20stood%20watchfully%20at%20checkpoints%20on%20every%20street%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Police%20officers%20keep%20watch%20at%20security%20checkpoints%20outside%20the%20hotel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683d790a6ffb6822ec61dec8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPolice%20kept%20watch%20at%20the%20main%20entrance.%3Cp%3EMOHD%20RASFAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20inside%20the%20building%2C%20security%20was%20surprisingly%20low-key.%20A%20freely%20accessible%20mezzanine%20opened%20up%20to%20a%20sprawling%20lobby%20where%20suits%20and%20one-stars%20mingled.%20In%20the%20lounge%2C%20sunlight%20spilled%20through%20the%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20as%20ministers%20held%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20checkpoints%20at%20the%20hotel's%20entrance%2C%20where%20regular%20guests%20were%20still%20allowed%20to%20enter.%20Several%20asked%20me%20for%20directions%20as%20they%20wandered%20by%20with%20flip-flops%20and%20shopping%20bags.%20A%20few%20feet%20from%20where%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20met%20with%20the%20Thai%20delegation%20on%20Friday%2C%20two%20people%20were%20playing%20tennis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20never%20happen%20in%20D.C.%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20American%20reporter%20who%20flew%20in%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20press%20corps%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20second-floor%20view%20of%20the%20Shangri-La%20hotel%20lobby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683d5377ca50259add4d6c22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shangri-La's%20lobby%20lounge%20was%20filled%20with%20officials%20and%20officers%20sipping%20on%20%249%20sodas%20and%20%2415%20teas.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Loh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPast