-secretly-working-multiple-remote-jobs-early-retirement-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20her%20retirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20put%20money%20toward%20a%20side%20business%20teaching%20arts%20and%20crafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20taken%20the%20second%20job%20without%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20was%20more%20about%20fulfilling%20something%2C%20adding%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20spoken%20to%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20Americans%20who%20are%20working%20multiple%20jobs%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-remote-worker-student-loan-debt-arizona-millennial-side-hustle-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20their%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-remote-california-cost-mounjaro-zepbound-without-insurance-weight-loss-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafford%20expensive%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-remote-worker-early-retirement-savings-jobs-work-california-data-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20for%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20many%20appreciated%20the%20extra%20income%2C%20they%20said%20it%20can%20come%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-remote-jobs-gives-financial-security-100-hour-week-burnout-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7f758e5-5d20-4853-acf4-e87730d006f5%5C%22%3EWorking%20on%20her%20side%20business%20helps%20her%20manage%20stress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Rivera%20began%20working%20as%20a%20production%20manager%20at%20BPI%20Outdoors%2C%20a%20sporting%20goods%20manufacturer.%20In%202020%2C%20she%20was%20coaching%20the%20operations%20manager%20of%20Quake%20Industries%20%E2%80%94%20a%20brand%20operated%20by%20BPI%20Outdoors%20%E2%80%94%20on%20ways%20to%20improve%20processes%20when%20this%20person%20left%20the%20company%2C%20and%20this%20position%20became%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivera%20said%20the%20CEO%20of%20BPI%20at%20the%20time%20asked%20her%20if%20she'd%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20on%20the%20extra%20job%20because%20of%20her%20expertise%20and%20the%20time%20she%20had%20spent%20coaching%20the%20previous%20manager.%20After%20thinking%20it%20over%20and%20negotiating%20her%20pay%20increase%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20accept%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivera%20said%20juggling%20two%20jobs%20was%20particularly%20difficult%20when%20she%20started%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupply-chain-crisis-when-it-will-be-over-end-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-related%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20she%20said%20she's%20streamlined%20processes%20over%20time%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20make%20her%20workload%20more%20manageable.%20She%20added%20that%20having%20insight%20into%20both%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20which%20sources%20parts%20from%20the%20other%20%E2%80%94%20has%20enabled%20smarter%20inventory%20planning.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20she%20sees%20BPI%20is%20running%20low%20on%20parts%20it%20gets%20from%20Quake%2C%20she%20can%20help%20adjust%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivera's%20main%20strategy%20for%20reducing%20the%20stress%20of%20working%20two%20jobs%20is%20one%20that%20she%20acknowledges%20sounds%20counterintuitive%3A%20She's%20taken%20on%20a%20third%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20handle%20my%20extra%20stress%20through%20my%20own%20personal%20business%20%E2%80%94%20by%20taking%20on%20more%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20spare%20time%2C%20Rivera%20makes%20crochet%20items%20like%20hats%20and%20blankets.%20She%20also%20has%20an%20Etsy%20store%20where%20she%20sells%20her%20handmade