20it%20%E2%80%94%20fresh%2C%20local%20fish%20full%20of%20flavour.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20taste%20%E2%80%94%20Paa%20Saa%20is%20a%20beautiful%20part%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20identity%2C%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaa%20Saa%20is%20comfort%20in%20a%20bowl%20%E2%80%94%20a%20warm%2C%20aromatic%20fish%20soup%20that%20starts%20with%20700%20ml%20of%20water%20gently%20simmered%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20salt%2C%20chopped%20ginger%2C%20and%20garlic.%20A%20spoonful%20of%20red%20chili%20paste%20adds%20just%20the%20right%20kick%2C%20while%20chunks%20of%20fresh%20bhetki%20fish%20soak%20up%20all%20that%20flavour%20as%20they%20cook%20slowly%20for%20about%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20it%20extra%20special%3F%20The%20lovely%20green%20tint%20and%20earthy%20flavour%20from%20Khumpatt%20leaves!%20Add%20in%20some%20bamboo%20shoots%2C%20leafy%20greens%2C%20and%20seasonal%20veggies%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20monsoon%20favorite%20that%E2%80%99s%20wholesome%20and%20soul-soothing.%20Best%20served%20hot%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20perfect%20dish%20to%20cozy%20up%20with%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%20in%20Arunachal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8U7iGYqsqbc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Khichuri%20rice%20and%20brinjal%20fry%2C%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20monsoon%20clouds%20gather%20over%20West%20Bengal%2C%20homes%20fill%20with%20the%20comforting%20aroma%20of%20Khichuri%2C%20a%20beloved%20rice%20and%20lentil%20dish.%20Often%20accompanied%20by%20Beguni%2C%20crispy%20fried%20brinjal%20slices%20dipped%20in%20a%20seasoned%20gram%20flour%20batter%2C%20this%20combination%20becomes%20a%20soul-soothing%20meal%20cherished%20across%20Bengali%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prepare%20a%20delicious%20%3Cem%3Ekhichuri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20start%20by%20dry%20roasting%20moong%20dal.%20Meanwhile%2C%20soak%20the%20rice%20in%20water%20for%20at%20least%20two%20to%20three%20hours.%20In%20a%20pan%2C%20heat%20five%20to%20six%20ablespoons%20of%20mustard%20oil%20and%20fry%20assorted%20vegetables%20individually%20for%20about%2010%20minutes%2C%20then%20set%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20large%20pan%2C%20heat%20five%20to%20six%20tablespoons%20of%20mustard%20oil%20for%20that%20pungent%20mustard%20kick%20is%20a%20signature%20of%20Bengali%20cooking!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELightly%20fry%20your%20veggies%20%E2%80%94%20potatoes%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20carrots%20%E2%80%94%20one%20by%20one%20until%20they%E2%80%99re%20slightly%20golden.%20Set%20them%20aside%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20pan%2C%20heat%20a%20little%20more%20mustard%20oil%20(about%203%20to%204%20tablespoons).%20Add%20a%20couple%20of%20bay%20leaves%20and%20a%20spoonful%20of%20ginger%20paste.%20Give%20it%20a%20quick%20saut%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToss%20in%20some%20chopped%20tomatoes%20and%20a%20splash%20of%20water.%20Now%20add%20your%20soaked%20rice%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20turmeric%20powder%20%E2%80%94%20this%20gives%20khichuri%20its%20signature%20golden%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMix%20in%20the%20roasted%20moong%20dal%20and%20pour%20enough%20water%20to%20cook%20everything%20gently%20(think%20soft%20and%20porridge-like).%20Let%20it%20simmer%20on%20medium%20heat%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20the%20fried%20veggies%20back%20into%20the%20pan%2C%20cover%2C%20and%20let%20everything%20bubble%20together%20for%20another%2010%20minutes.%20Your%20kitchen%20should%20smell%20amazing%20by%20now!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStir%20in%20a%20generous%20spoon%20of%20ghee%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20frozen%20peas.%20Add%20some%20slit%20green%20chilies%20if%20you%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Beguni%2C%20slice%20brinjals%20into%20thin%20rounds%2C%20sprinkle%20with%20salt%20and%20turmeric%2C%20and%20let%20them%20sit%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20Heat%20oil%20in%20a%20pan%20and%20fry%20until%20crispy%20and%20golden%20brown%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServe%20hot%20with%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%20on%20top!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20monsoon!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Saumya%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748673000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D441542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indulge%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20flavours%20with%20delightful%20dishes%20like%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20immunity-boosting%20Karkidaka%20Kanji%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20savoury%20Pundi%20Gatti%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20crispy%20Egg%20Bonda%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20aromatic%20Paa%20Saa%20soup%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20comforting%20Khichuri%20with%20brinjal%20fry.%20Perfect%20companions%20for%20rainy%20days!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F441542%2Ffive-tasty-monsoon-recipes-india-arunachal-kerala-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Old%20Buildings%2C%20New%20Fixes%3A%2010%20Sustainable%20%26amp%3B%20Affordable%20Innovations%20to